Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.31,0:03:02.31,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.31,0:03:04.66,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,We caught a cool shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:06.16,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Put it in! Put it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:08.00,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Put it in the fish tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:09.36,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Put it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.36,0:03:10.52,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Get in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.02,0:03:17.48,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Another one came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.48,0:03:18.28,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,A shark.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:20.38,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Well, isn't this room perfect?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.99,0:03:24.05,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,The room is fine, but a shark?! Those idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.46,0:03:26.01,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Alright, let's go see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:27.59,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Let's see the tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.59,0:03:30.50,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Hey! Did the shark get in?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.50,0:03:32.39,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,It's the one with the big horns!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.07,0:03:34.97,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Yes, it did, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.97,0:03:38.24,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,All the fish you caught so far are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.97,0:03:43.40,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,That was obviously going to happen when you think about the consequences!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.44,0:03:47.59,Captions,,0,0,220,,{\fad(150,350)}The ship continues its\Nfavorable voyage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:44.91,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,{\an8}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:47.01,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,{\an8}Turn this bastard into dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.01,0:03:50.08,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sanji! Make BBQ out of this stupid shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:51.24,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wait up, you novice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.88,0:03:54.05,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,This is a fresh fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.05,0:03:57.66,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Maybe some sushi... boiling it adding some spicy vinegar miso...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.66,0:03:59.12,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Tempura could also be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.49,0:04:02.10,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'm getting hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.61,0:04:07.29,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,That was a nice bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.79,0:04:11.60,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Hey! Something's floating in the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.87,0:04:13.62,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.64,0:04:15.77,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,A barrel?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.89,0:04:18.76,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,It has "treasure" written on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:24.12,Captions,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(372,506)\frz305.5\org(362,462)}Tribute to the Sea-God
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:21.32,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:22.01,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.01,0:04:24.11,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Some lost stuff from a treasure ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.35,0:04:25.42,Main,Usopp & Chopper,0,0,0,,Treasure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.19,0:04:33.13,Main,All,0,0,0,,{\i1}Treasure, treasure, we've discovered a treasure!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.13,0:04:34.67,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,It's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.06,0:04:37.19,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,It seems to be liquor and food supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:39.69,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,How can you tell without looking inside?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:43.19,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,It has " Tribute to the Sea-God" written on it, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:47.84,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,That's a floating barrel someone sends when they pray to have a safe trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.84,0:04:51.10,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,These offerings are sent to receive the sea's divine blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:53.68,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,In short, the word "tribute" means "to God".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:57.38,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,What, so it was pointless picking it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.98,0:05:00.09,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,After all it's booze, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.09,0:05:00.81,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Let's drink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.81,0:05:03.05,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Idiot! You'll get punished!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:05.52,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,You'll be fine as long as you pray, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.90,0:05:07.82,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,I won't pray to some God.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.82,0:05:12.86,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,It's said that liquor which is cared for by the sea waves has an exceptional taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.65,0:05:15.46,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,That's something we must taste!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.94,0:05:18.16,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Alright! Let's have a toast!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.51,0:05:23.67,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,After drinking it, we're supposed to refill the barrel with new offerings and set it adrift again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.64,0:05:25.88,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Open it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:26.81,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.81,0:05:30.28,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Hey, God! We'll be receiving this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.05,0:05:33.85,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,What God?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.85,0:05:38.25,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Who was the one that beat the hell out of this "God" at the Sky Island...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.69,0:05:40.16,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Alright! It's open!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.43,0:05:42.50,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Something flew out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.09,0:05:48.26,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:51.23,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,A red light...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:53.74,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.74,0:05:54.83,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.24,0:05:59.87,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,The liquor flew out, sparkled and then disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:01.75,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,It was a flare.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:02.77,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,A flare?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.35,0:06:06.64,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Could it be a curse from the Sea-God?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.16,0:06:10.19,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,It might have been just a prank, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.19,0:06:11.71,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.71,0:06:15.78,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Someone might be tracking this ship from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.78,0:06:17.82,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,N-No way...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.82,0:06:20.15,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Some sort of trap?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:25.10,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,By opening the barrel, we've informed someone that we're here?! {maybe it could be reworded, like "We've informed someone that we're here by opening the barrel?!"}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.10,0:06:26.79,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,We really can't see anyone one, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.39,0:06:28.49,Thoughts,Nami,0,0,0,,This atmospheric pressure...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:30.13,Thoughts,Nami,0,0,0,,The cloud currents are moving really fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.23,0:06:33.77,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,I can't see anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:35.74,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Nothing here either!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.74,0:06:37.20,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Everyone, to your posts!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:38.98,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Head south-southeast!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.98,0:06:41.41,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,A great storm is approaching within five minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.41,0:06:42.77,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I can't see it but,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.77,0:06:46.14,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,If she says so, it must be very close! {shouldn't it be "I can't see it," as 1st line and "but if she says so, it must be very close!" as 2nd line?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.14,0:06:47.72,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Nami, which way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.72,0:06:49.42,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,2 o'clock ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:06:59.11,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,It's no use!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.11,0:07:00.71,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,We're facing a head wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.71,0:07:02.12,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,We're being pushed back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.45,0:07:04.29,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.29,0:07:06.57,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Do you really think {\i1}this{\i0} is all this boat can handle?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.79,0:07:08.26,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.26,0:07:10.42,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Everyone raise the sails!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.42,0:07:11.96,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,We're bringing out the paddle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:14.31,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,That?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.40,0:07:17.58,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I really like that! It's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:19.70,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Soldier Dock System!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.70,0:07:21.00,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Channel Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.74,0:07:25.04,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Cola Engine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:27.23,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Paddle Ship Sunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:31.40,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.82,0:07:35.97,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.54,0:07:45.64,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,We made it through...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.64,0:07:47.85,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,We made it through, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.85,0:07:49.85,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,What's with this sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.22,0:07:52.58,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,It's not even night, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.58,0:07:56.05,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,This eerie fog has made everything dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.05,0:07:57.35,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.35,0:08:00.66,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,We've ventured into that sea area...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:02.59,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,We're not prepared yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.66,0:08:05.86,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,We've already arrived at the Fishman Island?
