Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.17,0:08:11.17,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.17,0:08:12.84,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Don't let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:17.56,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Without a doubt... this area is already... the famous... {already?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.56,0:08:20.18,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Florian Triangle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:24.75,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,The outrageous sea where everything mysteriously disappears!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.78,0:08:28.72,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Eh?! G-Gho... G-Gho...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:32.82,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Ghosts come out, right in this sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.06,0:08:34.46,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Stop joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.46,0:08:39.13,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,How come everyone besides me knows about that story?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.46,0:08:43.39,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,We heard it from Old Lady Kokoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.39,0:08:45.29,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,There are living skeletons here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:48.54,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,L-Living skeletons?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.16,0:08:53.97,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,That's just your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.97,0:08:55.98,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Don't scare him over such absurd stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:08:58.32,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Listen, Usopp.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.57,0:09:04.91,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Every year, more than 100 ships mysteriously vanish within this very sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.91,0:09:11.28,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Moreover, it is said that a ghost ship with the souls of deceased people wanders this sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.46,0:09:13.17,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,I don't want that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.17,0:09:14.97,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,You should've said that earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.97,0:09:17.62,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,And what if I had?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:19.39,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,I would be prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.39,0:09:21.63,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Prepared some items to disperse the evil spirits!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.63,0:09:25.31,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Usopp, lend me some of them too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.47,0:09:29.30,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,What's this voice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.98,0:09:38.68,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,It appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.58,0:09:42.83,Main,All,0,0,0,,{\i1}The ghost ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.64,0:09:54.34,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,What's with this song?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:56.46,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,It's the song of evil spirits!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.46,0:09:57.16,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Don't listen to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.16,0:09:59.61,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Close your ears or you'll be cursed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.93,0:10:04.12,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,No matter what kind of thing the ghost says to you, don't listen to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.47,0:10:07.32,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,If you answer back, he'll drag you to sea with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.32,0:10:10.12,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Evil spirits are always hunting travelers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.99,0:10:19.73,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Who could be... riding this ship...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:24.04,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,If he's an enemy, I'll just chop his head off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:26.56,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Something... is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:30.07,Jungle P lyrics,Brook,0,0,0,,{\i1}Going to deliver...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.04,0:10:35.25,Jungle P lyrics,Brook,0,0,0,,{\i1}Binks' Sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.23,0:10:56.01,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Why do I have to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.52,0:10:58.20,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,I wanna go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:11:01.26,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,That's why I told you I'd go by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:02.46,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.46,0:11:05.88,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,What if our ship gets cursed because of your stupidity?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.42,0:11:09.19,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,I had terrible luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.22,0:11:13.86,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Nami-san, it's alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.86,0:11:16.12,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,I'll protect you, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.12,0:11:20.05,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Nami, you wanted to find the treasure ship, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.05,0:11:22.11,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,There's no way this is a treasure ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:23.28,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,You saw it, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:24.73,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,That moving skeleton!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.00,0:11:27.80,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,He must be the treasure's guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.80,0:11:29.75,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's look for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.44,0:11:54.51,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Evil spirits, begone! Evil spirits, begone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.51,0:11:56.29,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Luffy, rest in peace...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.02,0:12:06.22,Captions,,0,0,220,,{\fad(600,600)}Skeleton Gentleman\NBrook
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.63,0:12:03.05,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nice to meet you! Yohohoho!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.05,0:12:08.14,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,{\an8}Forgive my discourtesy, I couldn't greet you when we first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.14,0:12:09.87,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,{\an8}You surprised me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:13.66,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's been many decades since the last time I met a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.66,0:12:16.66,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ship after ship, it's the same, just ghost ships wandering around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.66,0:12:18.57,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's kind of scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.57,0:12:21.62,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,{\an8}Well, make yourselves at home and come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.62,0:12:23.05,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,{\an8}We'll be able to talk more relaxed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.05,0:12:25.15,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Look, it's talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.15,0:12:27.71,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,The afro-skeleton is talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.71,0:12:29.06,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.29,0:12:31.90,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,My, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.37,0:12:37.17,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,What a lovely young lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.17,0:12:38.30,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Beautiful indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:41.11,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Eh... no... not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.06,0:12:45.38,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I have a good eye for beautiful ladies!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.38,0:12:48.36,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Although, skeletons don't have eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.67,0:12:57.50,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Can you please show me your panties?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:12:58.50,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,As if!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.57,0:13:02.17,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,My, my, quite a harsh one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.68,0:13:05.48,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,The flesh came right off of my bones...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.48,0:13:07.05,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Although I'm only a skeleton.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:08.15,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.09,0:13:12.59,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Hey, can you poop?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.59,0:13:15.01,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,There are plenty of other questions to ask besides that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.32,0:13:16.75,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Yes, I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.75,0:13:18.98,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,There's no need to answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.98,0:13:19.90,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Nevermind that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:25.55,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Firstly! Although you're nothing but bones, how can you be alive and talk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.55,0:13:27.92,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,What exactly are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.92,0:13:29.63,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.63,0:13:31.79,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,What's happening on this ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.79,0:13:34.50,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,And what's happening on this sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:35.54,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Answer all of this now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:37.08,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Nevermind all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.08,0:13:37.86,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Hey you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.03,0:13:40.70,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Join my crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.64,0:13:44.59,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Sure, why not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.55,0:14:06.59,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.59,0:14:10.43,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I'm afraid that while traveling, my ship ran into quite a bit of trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.43,0:14:12.90,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I am "Just Dead Bones" Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.90,0:14:14.05,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.32,0:14:15.38,Main,all,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.38,0:14:16.52,Main,all,0,0,0,,Who is this guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.43,0:14:19.39,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Oh my, oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.39,0:14:20.50,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,How harsh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:22.47,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,It's a skeleton!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:28.97,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Oh, what a beautiful woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.97,0:14:31.32,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Would you allow me to see your panties?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.32,0:14:32.92,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Stop it, you perverted skeleton!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.26,0:14:37.16,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Damn it! Skeletons can't talk, or walk, or have afros!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.16,0:14:38.19,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,This is a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.19,0:14:39.59,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,It's gotta be a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.59,0:14:41.13,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.13,0:14:43.66,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,What a relief... just a dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:46.77,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Hey, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.77,0:14:48.11,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,What's with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.11,0:14:49.31,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Isn't he funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.31,0:14:50.58,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,He's part of our crew now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.58,0:14:52.40,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,I don't care, I won't let him be!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.25,0:14:56.38,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Why the hell did you guys go with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.38,0:14:59.35,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Wasn't it to stop him from doing something like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.35,0:15:00.62,Main,both,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.36,0:15:05.16,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,It's nothing to get so worked up about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.16,0:15:06.49,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Let's go inside now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.49,0:15:07.83,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,We can have dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.16,0:15:09.80,Main,all,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who are you to decide that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.22,0:15:16.01,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Oh, what a wonderful dining room!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:17.61,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,And the kitchen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.24,0:15:20.28,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,This is such a marvelous ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:25.46,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's 'cuz this super guy made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.46,0:15:27.97,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,You've really got an eye for quality.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.13,0:15:30.68,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Hey, don't get attached to him, Franky.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.94,0:15:34.24,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,But what I'm truly looking forward to is the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:38.03,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I haven't had any good food for so many years...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.61,0:15:46.04,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I've lived so long with these hunger pains that I feared I was just skin and bones...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.33,0:15:51.28,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Although I'm a skeleton and don't have any skin at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.62,0:15:54.70,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Skull joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.53,0:16:03.17,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,As a gentleman, I enjoy the time spent awaiting my meal...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.47,0:16:05.54,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Dinner, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.47,0:16:05.54,Secondary,Luffy,0,0,0,,Food! Food!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:08.61,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Chef, please bring me some milk to drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.61,0:16:10.45,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Just shut up and wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.71,0:16:12.35,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,So anyway, Korobokle...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.61,0:16:14.78,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Oh no, it's Brook.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:19.92,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry, but I'm afraid I don't yet have your name...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.92,0:16:21.05,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.05,0:16:22.45,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'm Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.45,0:16:24.22,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,So, anyway, what are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.52,0:16:27.20,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,You two didn't even ask that kind of thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.45,0:16:30.87,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,We can get rid of the skeleton later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.87,0:16:32.19,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Right now, it's time to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.19,0:16:33.66,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,An entire octopus meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.66,0:16:35.44,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,It looks good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.44,0:16:38.03,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Hey, Brook, make sure you eat a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.03,0:16:40.28,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Sanji's food is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.73,0:16:43.07,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Oh, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.73,0:16:46.57,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I'm afraid that my heart is even emptier than my stomach...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.97,0:16:50.29,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,My fair lady, your portion seems to be a little large.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.29,0:16:51.61,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Would you care to trade?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.96,0:16:54.06,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,There's a lot more left, so just eat your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.23,0:16:58.47,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,The Revival Fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.47,0:17:00.70,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,So you ate a devil fruit....
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.52,0:17:03.33,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.92,0:17:07.86,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, I died once years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.86,0:17:09.59,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,First, clean your face off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:11.10,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,How'd you get yourself so dirty?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.61,0:17:13.43,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,The Revival Fruit...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.90,0:17:18.74,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Grants the ability to resurrect, so as a "resurrection human"â€¦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.40,0:17:22.84,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,You have the promise of a second life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.84,0:17:24.72,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,It's quite a mysterious ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.72,0:17:31.25,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Yes, at that time, I was a pirate just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.25,0:17:31.98,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.09,0:17:34.55,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.76,0:17:39.89,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,I just wanna beat some manners into you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:44.96,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:47.08,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,On the ship I was on before,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.63,0:17:52.25,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,The crew I was a part of came to this sea of devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:53.54,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.54,0:17:57.51,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Unluckily for us, incredibly powerful foes appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.71,0:18:01.85,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Our whole crew was killed in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.72,0:18:09.70,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I, of course, died as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.19,0:18:16.57,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,When I was alive, the Revival Fruit simply made me unable to swim...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.17,0:18:21.68,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,However, that day the fruit became more than just that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.50,0:18:25.42,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,My soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.42,0:18:29.22,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Has returned from the underworld to this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.03,0:18:40.20,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,If I was able to find my body quickly, I would have been revived.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.20,0:18:46.93,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,However, as you can see, the fog makes this sea difficult to navigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.93,0:18:49.47,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I became lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:55.57,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I searched for my body as a lost soul for an entire year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:19:02.49,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,And finally, I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.24,0:19:08.46,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,However, my body had been reduced to nothing but bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:15.13,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,When I saw it, my eyes widened very much in surprise...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.32,0:19:17.40,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Although I have no eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.64,0:19:20.59,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,You're so stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.59,0:19:22.37,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,You got lost just like Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:23.94,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.94,0:19:27.13,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,So that's when you became a talking skeleton?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.13,0:19:32.64,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,I didn't know a devil fruit could even bring someone back to life...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.64,0:19:37.24,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,But even after you come back to life, you're still unable to swim,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.24,0:19:39.45,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,so now you're just cursed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.45,0:19:43.18,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,But normally hair can't grow on bones...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.18,0:19:45.29,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,I've never seen a skeleton with an afro before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.29,0:19:47.52,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Oh, I just had strong roots.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.52,0:19:49.27,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Whatever you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:51.72,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,So, that means you aren't a ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.72,0:19:53.46,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,You're human?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:55.16,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Even though you're not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.16,0:19:57.76,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Yes, I dislike ghosts myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.76,0:20:00.03,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,If I see one, I cry out in fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.03,0:20:01.35,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Have you ever looked in a mirror?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.35,0:20:04.62,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,No, not a mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.62,0:20:06.95,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,H-Hey, w-wait a s-sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.95,0:20:08.72,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Y-You...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.01,0:20:10.69,Main,both,0,0,0,,Why don't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.69,0:20:13.67,Main,both,0,0,0,,Why don't you have a reflection in the mirror?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.13,0:20:18.38,Main,all,0,0,0,,A vampire?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.22,0:20:20.42,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.42,0:20:21.90,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.65,0:20:24.13,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,N-Now that you mention it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.59,0:20:26.14,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,You don't have a shadow either!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.14,0:20:27.42,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,He's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.42,0:20:29.87,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,What are you really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.77,0:20:37.20,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Why are you so calm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.20,0:20:39.55,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,W-We're all really scared here! Because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.60,0:20:43.14,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I'll tell you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.14,0:20:48.49,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I've been traveling this sea for so many years...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.91,0:20:55.37,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,However, me being a skeleton and having no shadow are two unrelated matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.17,0:20:59.39,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,To be continued.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.39,0:21:00.87,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,No, tell us {\i1}now{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.24,0:21:06.44,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,My shadow was stolen from me years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.44,0:21:07.58,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Stolen?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.27,0:21:08.95,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Your shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.56,0:21:14.58,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,After seeing you here living and talking, I'm not really surprised by anything you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.58,0:21:16.79,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,But can that really happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.79,0:21:18.95,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Yes, it can.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.95,0:21:25.06,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Having my shadow stolen from me means that I am no longer able to exist in the world's light.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.06,0:21:28.18,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,If I were to be hit with the light of the sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.18,0:21:30.03,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,My body would...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.87,0:21:34.92,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1500)}My body would disintegrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.58,0:21:45.45,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I once saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.45,0:21:51.16,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Someone with this same curse disappear when bathed in sunlight...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.16,0:21:55.30,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,It was enough to make my hair stand on end!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.30,0:21:57.49,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Although I'm a skeleton.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.36,0:22:02.57,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,A shadow is reflected on the ground by sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.57,0:22:11.48,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Therefore, I myself cannot be reflected in something like a mirror or photograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.48,0:22:16.95,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,And here I exist, unable to be in light, with all my crewmates long dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.48,0:22:20.20,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Your life's been pretty miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.20,0:22:22.86,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,But I lived through it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.86,0:22:24.60,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Even though I'm just bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.60,0:22:26.84,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I'm "Just Dead Bones" Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.84,0:22:28.06,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.06,0:22:29.79,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Why're you so happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.99,0:22:35.84,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Hey hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.84,0:22:36.47,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.45,0:22:41.85,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Today is such a marvelous day!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.85,0:22:43.80,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,465)}I've seen people once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.13,0:22:48.98,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,For so many years I've sailed through this ocean,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.98,0:22:50.68,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,The fog making it so dark I couldn't even tell when the days passed...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.23,0:22:58.06,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,All my crewmates were dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.59,0:23:02.19,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I was all alone on a ship that couldn't steer...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.08,0:23:07.06,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Sailing aimlessly for many, many years...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.99,0:23:12.07,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I was {\i1}so{\i0} lonely!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.74,0:23:13.87,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,So very lonely,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.21,0:23:15.61,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,And so very scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.90,0:23:17.57,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I just wanted to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.14,0:23:23.48,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,But I lived on...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.97,0:23:25.51,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,People are my happiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.51,0:23:29.39,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,All of you are my joy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.01,0:23:34.06,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I'm so happy that I would cry if I were able!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.02,0:23:37.79,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,You asked me to join your crew, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.79,0:23:40.92,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,That made me very happy, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.29,0:23:44.56,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,However, I must refuse your offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.56,0:23:46.50,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.16,0:23:53.87,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,As I told you before, my shadow was stolen, and I am unable to return to the light of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.87,0:23:58.64,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Right now I'm being protected by the fog of this devils' sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.64,0:23:59.48,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.48,0:24:05.25,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,If I were to leave this ocean with you, it would only be a matter of time before my body disappeared. {should this and the previous line be merged?}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.25,0:24:10.59,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I'll stay here, waiting for the joyous day when I can regain my shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.42,0:24:15.49,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,What are you going on about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.49,0:24:18.20,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,If you need your shadow, I'll get it back for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.91,0:24:21.32,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,You said someone stole it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.32,0:24:22.07,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.07,0:24:23.14,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.17,0:24:27.96,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,You are a very kind person.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.96,0:24:29.86,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I'm surprised...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.86,0:24:31.65,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,However, I won't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.45,0:24:37.79,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I can't tell you, who I've just met, to go and die for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.14,0:24:40.44,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Is the enemy really that strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.44,0:24:43.93,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,That's fine, but can't you at least tell us his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.93,0:24:45.84,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,No, I cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.84,0:24:47.80,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,You may find him if I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.10,0:24:54.78,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I don't know if I will find him before my second life is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.78,0:24:59.86,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,If I do find him, I've decided I will fight him, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.14,0:25:01.37,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,That aside...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.37,0:25:03.24,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Let's sing a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.25,0:25:08.73,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Music is my pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.73,0:25:11.46,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I was the musician on my crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.38,0:25:13.30,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.30,0:25:15.05,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,You're a musician?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.05,0:25:17.09,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Then you've really gotta join our crew, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.16,0:25:22.10,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Let's sing a fun song together!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.61,0:25:29.69,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Hey, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.69,0:25:30.41,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.95,0:25:32.39,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,G-G-G...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.42,0:25:34.81,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.81,0:25:37.11,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,There's something there!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.46,0:25:40.35,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,I'm scared, there's a ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.35,0:25:41.66,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.40,0:25:43.29,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,I'm getting out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.39,0:25:48.34,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Why're we shaking?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.15,0:25:50.09,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,No... it can't be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.11,0:25:53.33,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,What a thing to happen...!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.87,0:25:57.30,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Those guys're watching this ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.89,0:25:59.15,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Please look!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.15,0:26:01.61,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,This ship is being blocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.13,0:26:05.08,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,This is what caused that shaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.72,0:26:10.45,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,This is the back of the gate...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.45,0:26:11.65,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Gate?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.02,0:26:13.08,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Which means...!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.69,0:26:16.69,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Look at the back of the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.28,0:26:25.73,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.74,0:26:32.57,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Did you, perhaps, pick up a floating barrel...?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.86,0:26:35.91,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,We did!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.16,0:26:38.98,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,That was a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.98,0:26:42.15,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,This ship has been targeted since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.15,0:26:44.68,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.68,0:26:48.29,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,We've been right here the whole time...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.65,0:26:59.21,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Why is there an island there?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.21,0:27:02.93,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,That is the wandering ghost island...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.93,0:27:04.90,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Thriller Bark.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.64,0:27:12.19,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.19,0:27:14.73,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,The log pose isn't reacting at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.73,0:27:16.10,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.10,0:27:19.62,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,It is because this island traveled here from the distant West Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.50,0:27:25.01,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Oh, but today is such a lucky day.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.01,0:27:28.43,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Not only did I see people once more, but my deepest wish has come true as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.15,0:27:36.60,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,He's so light...!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.55,0:27:38.46,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.46,0:27:40.57,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Since I'm "just dead bones", I have to be light!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.32,0:27:46.28,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Now please, find a way to go through that gate behind you and leave this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.28,0:27:49.01,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Do not drop anchor here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.73,0:27:53.72,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I was so happy to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.72,0:27:56.99,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I will never forget your delicious food!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.99,0:27:58.16,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Farewell!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.16,0:28:00.46,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,If fate will have it, let us meet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.46,0:28:02.16,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Hey, wait, Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.16,0:28:03.80,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Didn't he eat a devil fruit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.80,0:28:05.93,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.05,0:28:10.42,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,He's running on the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.42,0:28:12.60,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Woah, cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.89,0:28:19.02,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,A-Anyway, Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.02,0:28:21.00,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Let's do what he said!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.00,0:28:25.23,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,We don't know what's going on here, but we do know that it's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.40,0:28:27.77,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.77,0:28:30.14,Main,all,0,0,0,,He's going!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,

